						               													<description>The Anthill Promo Tile was originally available in the Petrichor Honeybee Expansion Kickstarter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Shuffle the Anthill tile in with the chosen regular tiles for this game (before adding in any honey producing tiles, if using the Honeybee Expansion).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Once the tiles have been dealt out, place the 6 Ant tokens onto the Anthill tile.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whenever water drops land on the Anthill tile, all empty ant tokens pick up one drop each.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If, during your turn, you have at least one drop on an Ant token (on any tile), you may move that ant, and its drop, to an adjacent tile.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Drops on ants get harvested (if they are on a tile that gets harvested), and they count as drops on the tile where their ant is. Once its drop is harvested, the empty ant is returned to the Anthill tile.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
